Title: Send scheduled reports to all specified recipients
Level: 1
Component: reporting
Compatible: compat
Edition: cee
Version: 1.5.0p24
Date: 1576146308
Class: fix

Scheduled reports sent via email were only sent to the owner
of the report and not to the recipients specified in the field
"Email-Addresses to mail PDF reports to". This is fixed.

Reports that were executed manually by a user were not affected
by this issue.
